 with bacon, if desired.","Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> for the Chicken stock paste recipe.","You can use any variety of white cabbage in this recipe, however the cooking times may vary. Cook cabbage until just tender."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","35m","4 portions"]}